            follow.
          </p>

          <p class="welcome-message" style="padding-top: 40px">
            To get started, simply: Complete the account creation process by
            uploading all your Company Registration Documents.
            <h4>That's it!</h4>
          </p>
          <p class="welcome-message" style="padding-top: 40px">
            Don't worry, we'll also send friendly reminders in case anything
